    <h4 class="odd">DESCRIPTION</h4>

    <p class="even">With this module you can easily add 'About Us' page to your Website. You can also add sub-pages, as well as external links. <br> <br>
    </p>

    <h4 class="odd">INSTALL/UNINSTALL</h4>

    <p class="even">No special measures necessary, follow the standard installation process -
        extract the module folder into the ./modules directory. Install the module through
        Admin -> System Module -> Modules.<br><br>
        Detailed instructions on installing modules are available in the
        <a href="https://www.gitbook.com/book/xoops/xoops-operations-guide/" target="_blank">XOOPS Operations Manual</a></p>


